lead_paragraph: Paceman Kagiso Rabada led a brilliant South Africa bowling display that lifted the Proteas to a 47-run win over Australia in the triangular one-day international series in Guyana on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Brilliant Bowling Lifts South Africa to Win Over Australia
